# RootED K-12 Website

This is the source code for the official **RootED K-12** website, a dedicated education technology consulting firm based in Boston, Massachusetts. 

The site is hosted via GitHub Pages and is accessible at: [www.rootedk12.com](https://www.rootedk12.com)

## ğŸ¯ Our Mission
RootED K-12 serves as a partner in K-12 education technology. We collaborate across various sectors to bridge service divides, specializing in cybersecurity preparedness and ed-tech implementation, always keeping the best interests of students at the forefront.

