## ğŸš€ How to Make Updates
To update the live website:
1. Edit the files in this repository (e.g., updating the "Insights" or "News" sections).
2. Commit your changes to the `main` branch.
3. GitHub Actions will automatically trigger a build, and changes will reflect on the live domain within ~60 seconds.

